.SH "NAME"
packerix-modules \- packerix configuration options
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Theses are the modules you can use in your
config\&.nix
which are delivered by default by packerix\&.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.PP
You can use the following options in
config\&.nix:
.PP
